fields.name: Honey Comb Book Shelf
fields.description:
A bookshelf with a sleek, yet quirky design to make any space interesting.
Use it as a jazzy bookshelf or as a state of the art display case.
Change the orientation to suit your needs – the irregularly shaped shelves leave room for play.
Plenty of storage and display space.
